reviewText: During the last day or two before the end of a semester students have very little to do in the classroom. I put this up on the screen with captions in Spanish or in Spanish with captions in English. They enjoy the moment, but still learn some Spanish.
The movie it self was great, my 8 year loved it But the price was way,way to high
My 2 1/2 year old Grandson loves this movie! Actually I find it pretty funny!
